<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129696>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Rhytiphora species, dorsal and frontal (head only) views. A: Rhytiphora collaris female (ANIC 25-067050). B: Rhytiphora piperitia male (ANIC 25-058414). C–D: Rhytiphora argentata male (ANIC 25-061934). E: Rhytiphora garnetensis sp. nov. paratype male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129698>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Rhytiphora species, lateral view. A: Rhytiphora garnetensis sp. nov. holotype male (ANIC 25-074497). B: Rhytiphora delicatula male (ANIC 25-061931). C: Rhytiphora amicula male (ANIC 25-066535). D: Rhytiphora argentata male (ANIC 25-061934). E: Rhytiphora collaris female (ANIC 25-067050). F: Rhytiphora piperitia male (ANIC 25-058414)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129704>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Rhytiphora collaris group, type specimens. A: Platyomopsis delicatula McKeown, 1948 holotype male. B: Rhytiphora uniformis Blackburn, 1901 lectotype female. C: Rhytiphora maculosella Blackburn, 1902 lectotype female. D: Saperda collaris Donovan, 1805 neotype male. E: Rhytiphora (Setomopsis) vermiculosa Breuning, 1970 holotype female. F: Rhytiphora (Saperdopsis) parafarinosa Breuning, 1970 holotype female. G: Symphyletes compos Blackburn, 1902 lectotype male. H: Symphyletes vestigialis Pascoe, 1864 lectotype male. I: Rhytiphora amicula White, 1859 lectotype male. J: Rhytiphora piperitia Hope, 1842 lectotype female. K: Symphyletes humeralis White, 1858 lectotype. L: Rhytiphora truncata Breuning, 1940 holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129684>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Rhytiphora species, holotypes (A–J) and reference photos (K–L). A: Rhytiphora detrita male Hope, 1842. B: Mesiphiastus (Pubiphiastus) laterialbus female Breuning, 1970. C: Rhytiphora macleayi female Lea, 1912. D: Corrhenes (Corrhenes) paulla fuscosignata male Breuning, 1970. E: Acanthocinus piliger female Macleay, 1826. F: Rhytiphora piperitia female Hope, 1842. G: Menyllus rotundipennis male Breuning, 1968. H: Rhytiphora (Rhytiphora) subargentata male Breuning, 1970. I: Rhytiphora (Saperdopsis) tenimberensis male Breuning, 1973 [R. sundaensis]. J: Rhytiphora tuberculata male Hope, 1842. K: Rhytiphora rugicollis female (Dalman, 1817). L: Rhytiphora frenchiana female Breuning, 1961." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129684/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Rhytiphora paulla and similar species, holotypes. A: Corrhenes (Corrhenes) paulla fuscosignata male Breuning, 1970. B: Corrhenes (Corrhenes) paulla grisea male Breuning, 1963. C: Saperda funesta Pascoe, 1859. D: Cobria rufa male Breuning, 1961. E: Corrhenes flavovittata Breuning, 1938. F: Corrhenes (Corrhenes) flavovittata demarzi male Breuning, 1963 [R. rentzi]. G: Saperda stigmatica Pascoe, 1863. H: Corrhenes guttulata Pascoe, 1865. I: Saperda mystica male Pascoe, 1863." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129686>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Rhytiphora species, holotypes recovered by the Prague National Museum. A: Rhytiphora argentata female Breuning, 1938, dorsal. B: Rhytiphora obenbergeri male Breuning, 1938, dorsal. C: Rhytiphora (Saperdopsis) obsoleta female Breuning, 1938, dorsal. D: Rhytiphora argentata female Breuning, 1938, frontal. E: Rhytiphora argentata female Breuning, 1938, lateral. F: Rhytiphora obenbergeri male Breuning, 1938, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129682>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Rhytiphora species in their natural habitats. A: Rhytiphora albospilota Aurivillius, 1893, © P. Zborowski. B: Rhytiphora pardalina (Breuning, 1942), © P. Zborowski. C: Rhytiphora diva (Thomson, 1860), © J. Lochman. D: Rhytiphora nigrovirens (Donovan, 1805), © P. Zborowski. E: Rhytiphora lateralis (Pascoe, 1858), © S. Harris. F: Rhytiphora saundersii (Pascoe, 1857), © A. Sundholm. G: Rhytiphora dallasii Pascoe, 1869, © R. de Keyzer. H: Rhytiphora obliqua (Donovan, 1805), © R. de Keyzer." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129710>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Rhytiphora frenchi and similar species, holotypes (A–E) and reference photo (F). A: Platyomopsis frenchi female Blackburn, 1890. B: Symphyletes armatulus male White, 1859. C: Platyomopsis spinosa female Thomson, 1864. D: Platyomopsis multispinis male Breuning, 1938. E: Platyomopsis regularis female Gahan, 1893. F: Rhytiphora (Platyomopsis) subregularis Breuning, 1973." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129710/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129688>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Rhytiphora species, holotypes omitted from Ślipiński & Escalona (2013). A: Prosoplus (Prosoplus) demarzi female Breuning, 1963. B: Prosoplus elongatus female Breuning, 1938. C: Platyomopsis frenchi female Blackburn, 1890. D: Notocorrhenes freyi Breuning, 1961. E: Hathlia grammica Pascoe, 1859. F: Rhytiphora leucospila Gahan, 1893. G: Penthea lichenosus female McKeown, 1942. H: Xiphohathlia lobata male Breuning, 1961. I: Penthea macularia Pascoe, 1867. J: Sysspilotus macleayi Pascoe, 1865. K: Menyllus maculicornis Pascoe, 1864." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129688/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129712>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Rhytiphora scenica and similar species, holotypes. A: Penthea scenica Pascoe, 1863. B: Penthea lichenosus female McKeown, 1942. C: Penthea (Melanopenthea) obscura male Breuning, 1961. D: Penthea mastersi Blackburn, 1897. E: Penthea melanosticta Pascoe, 1875. F: Penthea pardalina female Breuning, 1942." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129712/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

